Of course.

1040
01:29:29,944 --> 01:29:31,935
Are you being serious?

1041
01:29:35,016 --> 01:29:37,348
Of course.

1042
01:29:50,632 --> 01:29:53,260
I came to say
we made a mistake.

1043
01:29:56,471 --> 01:29:58,405
Your mom's outside
waiting for you.

1044
