But not on your shoulder.

1049
01:30:21,396 --> 01:30:24,058
Right.

1050
01:30:44,853 --> 01:30:47,014
Does she really love him?

1051
01:30:49,124 --> 01:30:52,389
That's what the doctors say.

1052
01:30:56,998 --> 01:31:00,832
What about him?

1053
